Chapters: 1-7 The Phil Donahue Show (7-10-95)
w/ Special guest Max Wienberg

Excellent appearance by Ringo, who shows patience with
Phil and his exhuberant questioning.  Max Weinberg joins
the show for the second half.  He and Ringo share thoughts
about drumming.  Quite interestng.
